      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of lived-in charm that makes every drive feel like the start of a story. It\u2019s an honest, affordable ride for someone who sees potential where others see a blank canvas\u2014perfect as a first car, backup commuter, or weekend project. If you\u2019ve been looking for something with character, presence, and room to make it your own, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
