    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation with plenty of potential for the right buyer. It shows age and wear consistent with a well-used car, but it remains an appealing option for someone seeking an inexpensive commuter, first project, or backup vehicle. A practical opportunity to own at a low entry price.",
